Real trivial nit-pick one for you :)

When you go to resolve an issue, you see the text 'If you have permission to close issues, you can optionally resolve & close the issue at the same time'.

Jira knows whether or not you have this permission so should provide meaningful text for each case.  Secondly, how does this text work with a custom work flow...?
